reviewText: Great fighting skills for a four star movie. I like the movie because of the action in it. It is a must see movie if you are an kung fu fan.
Except for the picture, this movie was a great watch as well. The upsetting part when bits of scenes were cut in some ways. But still it was a great watch.

First off let me say that if you get the film with Meng Fei and Liang Kar Luang which is on the cover you will be getting a first class film, but the title and the actors advertised don't match. So to sum it up I will critque the cover not the film because I don't know what film you are getting.
